{"title":"JavaScript 解構拆解","uid":"a4a90a8544184246ae6c38f5f79f182a","slug":"解構拆解","date":"2021-03-15T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2022-06-13T13:59:22.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/解構拆解.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"解構拆解\"><a href=\"#解構拆解\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"解構拆解\"></a>解構拆解</h1><h3 id=\"語法：-三個點為收回剩下值\"><a href=\"#語法：-三個點為收回剩下值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"語法： ... 三個點為收回剩下值\"></a>語法： <code>...</code> 三個點為收回剩下值</h3><h3 id=\"方法一-slice\"><a href=\"#方法一-slice\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方法一 :  slice()\"></a>方法一 :  <code>slice()</code></h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F; 1.單獨刪減組裝用法\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 語法 slice() (切片)\n&#x2F;&#x2F; slice(0,3) 切分陣列 (含頭不含尾)!!\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 所以是切分順序從第 0 個到第 2 個 !!\nconst arr &#x3D; [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9];\nconst index &#x3D; 3;\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 要去除 index&#x3D;3 ,第四個數字(陣列第一個數字順序為0)\nconsole.log([...arr.slice(0, index), ...arr.slice(index + 1)]);\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F; arr &#x3D; [1,2,3,5,6,7,8,9]</code></pre>\n\n\n<h3 id=\"方法二-rest-使用新物件，去收回剩下數值\"><a href=\"#方法二-rest-使用新物件，去收回剩下數值\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"方法二 :    [...rest]  (使用新物件，去收回剩下數值)\"></a>方法二 :    <code>[...rest]</code>  (使用新物件，去收回剩下數值)</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">&#x2F;&#x2F; 拆解 object 以及組裝新的 object\nconst foo &#x3D; [&#39;a&#39;,&#39;b&#39;,&#39;c&#39;]    &#x2F;&#x2F;arr\nconst bar &#x3D; &#123;              &#x2F;&#x2F;object\n    a:1,\n    b:2,\n    c:3\n&#125;\n\nconst &#123; a &#125; &#x3D; bar \n&#x2F;&#x2F; a &#x3D; bar.x ; a &#x3D; 1\n\nconst &#123; a, ...rest&#125; &#x3D; bar\nconsole.log(&quot;rest&quot;,rest)\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 不要 a 數值，\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 建立新 object (rest) 來收回剩下的數值\n&#x2F;&#x2F; rest&#123;b:2,c:3&#125;\n\nconst &#123;x,y,...rest2&#125; &#x3D;foo\nconsole.log(x,y,rest2)\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 不要 x,y,建立新 object (rest2) 收回剩下的數值\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 因為 foo 為陣列 list 所以不會有命名，\n&#x2F;&#x2F; 但可以使用 rest2 去呼叫做重複使用\n&#x2F;&#x2F; x&#x3D;a,y&#x3D;b,rest2&#x3D;c\n\nconst &#123; x, y&#125; &#x3D; foo\n&#x2F;&#x2F; bar 為 object 型態\n&#x2F;&#x2F; </code></pre>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://codesandbox.io/s/jsspread-chonggouzuzhuang-tlv1l?file=/src/index.js\">以上 code 範例以及更多應用</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"splice\"><a href=\"#splice\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"splice()\"></a>splice()</h3><p>程式碼：</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>HTML:</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-htmlembedded\" data-language=\"htmlembedded\"><code class=\"language-htmlembedded\">&lt;ul style&#x3D;&quot;padding:50px;background:#000;color:#fff&quot; class&#x3D;&quot;list&quot;&gt;&lt;&#x2F;ul&gt;</code></pre>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p> JS:<br> <pre class=\"line-numbers language-javascript\" data-language=\"javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\">var country &#x3D; [\n  &#123;\n    farmer:&#39;卡斯伯&#39;\n  &#125;\n  ,&#123;\n    farmer:&#39;查理&#39;\n  &#125;,&#123;\n    farmer:&#39;約翰&#39;\n  &#125;\n]\nvar list &#x3D; document.querySelector(&#39;.list&#39;);\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F;更新農場資料\nfunction updateList()&#123;\n  var str &#x3D; &#39;&#39;;\n  var len &#x3D; country.length;\n  for(var i &#x3D; 0;len&gt;i;i++)&#123;\n    str+&#x3D;&#39;&lt;li data-num&#x3D;&quot;&#39;+i+&#39;&quot;&gt;&#39;+country[i].farmer+&#39;&lt;&#x2F;li&gt;&#39;\n  &#125;\n  list.innerHTML &#x3D; str;\n&#125;\nupdateList();\n\n&#x2F;&#x2F;確認點擊的農夫是誰\nfunction checkList(e)&#123;\n  var num &#x3D; e.target.dataset.num;\n  &#x2F;&#x2F; console.log(e.target.nodeName);\n  if(e.target.nodeName !&#x3D;&#x3D; &#39;LI&#39;)&#123;return&#125;;\n  country.splice(num,1);\n  updateList();\n&#125;\nlist.addEventListener(&#39;click&#39;,checkList,false);</code></pre></p></blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li>先執行updateList() 渲染畫面加上 ‘li’ 以及加上 data-num ，</li>\n<li>點擊事件觸發 checkList ，</li>\n<li>去 if 判斷 如果等於 ‘li’ ，</li>\n<li>就會 splice() 刪除點選的 ‘li’，</li>\n<li>再執行一次 update 渲染畫面，再次加上 ‘li’ 以及加上 data-num</li>\n</ol>\n","text":"解構拆解語法： ... 三個點為收回剩下值方法一 : slice()&#x2F;&#x2F; 1.單獨刪減組裝用法 &#x2F;&#x2F; 語法 slice() (切片) &#x2F;&#x2F; slice(0,3) 切分陣列 (含頭不含尾)!! &#x2F;&#x2F; 所...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.4k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":45,"path":"api/categories/JavaScript.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"JavaScript","slug":"JavaScript","count":39,"path":"api/tags/JavaScript.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E8%A7%A3%E6%A7%8B%E6%8B%86%E8%A7%A3\"><span class=\"toc-text\">解構拆解</span></a><ol class=\"toc-chi